33
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:02,759
You have to show up.

34
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,840
I'll go over right away.

35
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,919
But before I go,

36
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,120
