64
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,639
who the murderer is?

65
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:39,759
Tianhai Sect did it.

66
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:42,040
But they have so many people.

67
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:44,160
They can't all be murderers.

68
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,360
We need to investigate

69
00:04:47,079 --> 00:04:48,360
