Lin Pinghe.

94
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:31,639
He.

95
00:07:31,959 --> 00:07:33,839
Let's see what else you can do.

96
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:38,600
He.

97
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,959
You useless kid.

98
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:06,560
You traitor

99
