to send my dad off.

101
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,919
He was the first

102
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:37,840
but not the last.

103
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,879
Everyone related to my dad's death

104
00:08:40,879 --> 00:08:42,399
will pay with their lives.

105
00:08:58,159 --> 00:08:59,600
The last shot was fired by Ms. Jia?

106
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:00,560
Yes.

107
00:09:00,560 --> 00:09:01,320
Huan wanted to be

108
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,799
the leader and sold Lin Yongning out.

109
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:03,840
So,

110
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,639
Black Lotus Gang is going
the old path again.

111
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:06,240
Not just that.

112
00:09:06,240 --> 00:09:07,240
Given today's situation,

113
00:09:07,559 --> 00:09:08,919
Lin Pinghe wants to escalate it.

114
00:09:09,360 --> 00:09:10,200
Let's go

115
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,200
to meet Bobo.

116
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,919
Do you usually go fishing?

117
00:09:43,039 --> 00:09:43,919
What kind of fishing?

118
00:09:46,879 --> 00:09:47,919
What a shame.

119
00:09:50,679 --> 00:09:51,559
About what?

120
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:54,440
If you want to fish, come quickly.

121
00:09:55,559 --> 00:09:57,039
There won't be any fish here soon.

122
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:58,600
What do you mean?

123
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:01,759
Haven't you watched the news?

124
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,200
You mean that chemical plant?

125
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:08,320
So the pollution is serious.

126
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:09,840
The fish

127
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,039
can't stand it.

128
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:15,120
Humans might still do.

129
00:10:16,039 --> 00:10:18,559
Turns out Tianhai Sect has come and made

130
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,159
a high-profile move

131
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,519
for this.

132
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,560
That's right.

133
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,960
We'll rely on you in the future.

134
00:10:28,879 --> 00:10:30,000
For what?

135
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:32,360
The plan is approved,

136
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:33,639
but

137
00:10:33,639 --> 00:10:35,879
the relocation and renovation

138
00:10:36,639 --> 00:10:37,759
are very troublesome.

139
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:39,519
There are always people

140
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,600
who are not smart enough.

141
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:42,399
At such times,

142
00:10:42,399 --> 00:10:44,320
someone needs to talk to them.

143
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:46,559
Like how you talked to Lin Yongning?

144
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:56,000
According to your plan,

145
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,840
in the future,

146
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,559
this place might be different.

147
00:11:02,840 --> 00:11:04,600
Out with the old, in with the new.

148
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:07,559
If you're willing to cooperate,

149
00:11:09,360 --> 00:11:10,919
I'll give you a big favor.

150
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,119
How does it sound?

151
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:13,600
Let's hear it.

152
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,559
What big favor?

153
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,240
Why did you come to see me today?

154
00:11:41,679 --> 00:11:43,240
Business can wait.

155
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:45,399
If today is inconvenient for you,

156
00:11:45,639 --> 00:11:47,159
I can come again tomorrow.

157
00:11:47,759 --> 00:11:48,799
It's not necessary.

158
00:11:50,000 --> 00:11:51,200
It's convenient right now.

159
00:11:52,519 --> 00:11:53,559
He.

160
00:11:53,639 --> 00:11:54,639
You guys can go out.

161
00:12:04,039 --> 00:12:05,120
Actually,

162
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:07,279
