163
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,399
We just want the town

164
00:12:10,120 --> 00:12:11,759
not to be messed up by them.

165
00:12:12,679 --> 00:12:14,159
Say it however you want.

166
00:12:14,159 --> 00:12:15,320
It's the same meaning.

167
00:12:18,120 --> 00:12:19,720
Our Tianhai Sect is willing to help.

168
00:12:20,120 --> 00:12:21,120
But there are conditions,

169
00:12:21,679 --> 00:12:22,600
right?

170
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:24,600
What do you think?

171
00:12:30,320 --> 00:12:31,639
That shot just now

172
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:34,399
was a welcome gift from me.

173
00:12:44,879 --> 00:12:46,120
What do you want in return?

174
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,159
Did your dad tell you

175
00:12:51,159 --> 00:12:53,840
what kind of business he and I were in?

176
00:12:57,080 --> 00:12:58,159
No way.

177
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,120
Don't rush to refuse.

178
00:13:07,879 --> 00:13:09,240
Think it over.

179
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:12,320
Tourism is the foundation
of Lian'an Town.

180
00:13:13,480 --> 00:13:14,480
Once the chemical plant

181
00:13:15,039 --> 00:13:15,879
is built, as you say,

182
00:13:15,879 --> 00:13:17,120
we'll have to change careers.

183
00:13:18,039 --> 00:13:19,440
Do you think this is good?

184
00:13:21,159 --> 00:13:22,600
Well, the world is changing.

185
00:13:24,240 --> 00:13:26,120
Changing the way we live
isn't necessarily bad.

186
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,879
Whether it's good or not
is not up to us.

187
00:13:29,399 --> 00:13:30,279
You should ask

188
00:13:30,279 --> 00:13:31,759
whether the people here agree.

189
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:34,960
As far as I know, it seems

190
00:13:35,639 --> 00:13:36,479
they

191
00:13:37,440 --> 00:13:39,000
are not too willing to change.

192
00:13:41,919 --> 00:13:43,360
Then we have different opinions.

193
00:13:44,519 --> 00:13:45,600
But it doesn't matter.

194
00:13:46,600 --> 00:13:47,799
There's still plenty of time.

195
00:13:49,360 --> 00:13:50,200
Then,

196
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:52,039
I'll take my leave first.

197
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:56,639
Chen Tianshuang, right?

198
00:14:02,639 --> 00:14:03,960
Am I that famous?

199
00:14:08,639 --> 00:14:11,080
If you become the Chief,

200
00:14:11,840 --> 00:14:13,519
will you be stubborn like this?

201
00:14:15,639 --> 00:14:16,919
Someone like me

202
00:14:17,639 --> 00:14:18,639
can't become a big boss.

203
00:14:19,600 --> 00:14:21,000
Don't say it like that.

204
00:14:22,000 --> 00:14:23,559
Becoming a big boss isn't difficult.

205
00:14:25,480 --> 00:14:27,039
When there's no one above you,

206
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:28,759
you'll be the big boss.

207
00:14:38,600 --> 00:14:39,759
Just kidding.

208
00:14:40,919 --> 00:14:42,240
Go fishing with me sometime.

209
00:14:56,000 --> 00:14:57,440
Get it straight.

210
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:59,039
I'm the boss of Black Lotus Gang.

211
00:14:59,039 --> 00:15:00,120
What price did you offer?

212
00:15:00,200 --> 00:15:01,759
You get it straight.

213
00:15:02,720 --> 00:15:04,759
Don't think you're really the big boss

214
00:15:04,759 --> 00:15:06,799
just because of the way they call you.

215
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:09,200
There were so many here just now.

216
00:15:09,679 --> 00:15:11,559
But only one person helped you

217
00:15:11,879 --> 00:15:13,600
while the others were just onlookers.

218
00:15:14,399 --> 00:15:15,559
If there are benefits,

219
00:15:15,559 --> 00:15:17,480
others might see you as the boss.

220
00:15:18,279 --> 00:15:19,519
But if there aren't any,

221
00:15:19,519 --> 00:15:21,759
they'll fight to send you
to Tianhai Sect.

222
00:15:31,600 --> 00:15:32,519
What about you?

223
00:15:32,919 --> 00:15:35,159
I'm the last straw you can clutch at.

224
00:15:35,960 --> 00:15:37,320
You have no choice.

225
00:15:48,519 --> 00:15:49,359
Yes,

226
00:15:50,559 --> 00:15:51,759
I have no choice.

227
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,120
But neither do you.

228
00:15:54,799 --> 00:15:56,080
You have no choice, either.

229
00:16:00,039 --> 00:16:01,879
Don't think you can keep up appearances,

230
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:04,279
and that I don't know what you are.

231
00:16:05,240 --> 00:16:06,759
You could do nothing if no one

232
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:08,279
helped you in Taiwan, China.

233
00:16:09,200 --> 00:16:10,759
