234
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,120
why did you come to me?

235
00:16:14,279 --> 00:16:16,320
So I'm the last straw you can clutch at.

236
00:16:18,879 --> 00:16:20,159
You can't raise the price,

237
00:16:21,159 --> 00:16:22,679
but you'll have to lower it.

238
00:16:24,799 --> 00:16:26,080
You're insane.

239
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,240
If you don't work with me,

240
00:16:28,919 --> 00:16:31,360
when Tianhai Sect comes,
you'll be doomed.

241
00:16:32,279 --> 00:16:33,240
Tianhai Sect?

242
00:16:36,240 --> 00:16:37,080
Yes.

243
00:16:37,759 --> 00:16:39,159
I am insane.

244
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:41,000
But you're not.

245
00:16:41,399 --> 00:16:42,600
You can't win against me now.

246
00:16:43,279 --> 00:16:44,759
I can risk anything.

247
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,159
But can you?

248
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,519
I received news

249
00:17:00,519 --> 00:17:02,320
that Ms. Jia wanted to work
with Lin Pinghe.

250
00:17:02,320 --> 00:17:04,039
So we have to make a move soon.

251
00:17:05,119 --> 00:17:06,279
What about Lin Pinghe?

252
00:17:07,400 --> 00:17:09,319
Lin Pinghe has already asked
Tianhai Sect

253
00:17:09,839 --> 00:17:10,960
to hand over the murderer.

254
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,160
Or, he won't let them off.

255
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:14,440
Tianhai Sect hasn't responded.

256
00:17:14,799 --> 00:17:16,559
Let them fight if they want to.

257
00:17:16,720 --> 00:17:18,400
Can't we just sit back and watch?

258
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:19,759
The struggle and grudges

259
00:17:19,920 --> 00:17:20,760
within the gangs

260
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:22,599
have nothing to do with us.

261
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:25,960
But if they involve the people
of Lian'an Town,

262
00:17:26,480 --> 00:17:28,000
it'll be our business.

263
00:17:28,000 --> 00:17:29,759
How powerful is Tianhai Sect?

264
00:17:29,759 --> 00:17:31,359
We helplessly watched Lin Yongning

265
00:17:31,359 --> 00:17:32,559
die in front of us.

266
00:17:32,559 --> 00:17:34,519
Now Lin Pinghe is trying to fight them.

267
00:17:35,039 --> 00:17:36,519
I guess it won't be long

268
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:38,039
before Black Lotus Gang is gone.

269
00:17:38,359 --> 00:17:40,319
Why do we have to get involved
in this mess?

270
00:17:40,759 --> 00:17:41,960
I always talk about

271
00:17:42,880 --> 00:17:44,359
protecting the people of this town.

272
00:17:45,279 --> 00:17:46,519
Actually, it's to protect

273
00:17:47,240 --> 00:17:48,799
people I know and I don't.

274
00:17:49,319 --> 00:17:51,039
Honestly, I've been here for six years,

275
00:17:52,079 --> 00:17:53,720
and I care about them.

276
00:17:54,319 --> 00:17:55,559
Do you know what I mean?

277
00:17:56,839 --> 00:17:57,960
You've said so much.

278
00:17:58,599 --> 00:18:00,240
You just want me to deal with Ms. Jia.

279
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:03,839
You finally got the point.

280
00:18:05,079 --> 00:18:05,920
Tell me,

281
00:18:06,759 --> 00:18:07,720
how to put on this act?

282
00:18:08,079 --> 00:18:09,119
It's very simple.

283
00:18:10,880 --> 00:18:11,720
Pretend to cooperate

284
00:18:12,079 --> 00:18:13,319
with them and then

285
00:18:13,319 --> 00:18:14,359
catch them red-handed.

286
00:18:14,359 --> 00:18:15,160
Any details?

287
00:18:15,160 --> 00:18:16,200
Just tell her,

288
00:18:16,359 --> 00:18:18,039
Five Lakes Alliance will help her

289
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:20,480
transport goods
and take care of the trouble.

290
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:21,880
But due to its reputation,

291
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:23,559
we can't let too many people show up,

292
00:18:23,559 --> 00:18:24,440
and we need helpers.

293
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:25,720
Helpers?

294
00:18:25,960 --> 00:18:27,920
The police who arrested her at the time.

295
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,839
Almost forgot about the police.

296
00:18:30,759 --> 00:18:31,839
I can help you arrange

297
00:18:32,319 --> 00:18:33,640
for the next two steps.

298
00:18:33,759 --> 00:18:35,400
But whether you can gain her trust

299
00:18:36,039 --> 00:18:37,079
is up to you.

300
00:18:37,359 --> 00:18:38,799
Clearly, this is the hardest step.

301
00:18:39,880 --> 00:18:41,079
Last time when you came back,

302
00:18:41,079 --> 00:18:42,400
weren't you quite excited?

303
00:18:42,400 --> 00:18:44,200
Wasn't that just putting on a show?

304
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,519
So,

305
00:18:45,519 --> 00:18:47,720
Ms. Jia is an old hand.

306
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:49,200
You must make it convincing.

307
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:53,720
For the peace of Lian'an Town,

308
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:56,559
it seems I have to make a sacrifice.

309
00:18:56,934 --> 00:19:00,877
♪When the name is buried in dust♪

310
00:19:00,966 --> 00:19:04,288
♪There's still a heartbeat
piercing through dawn and dusk♪

311
00:19:04,422 --> 00:19:08,145
♪If there's no applause for the ending♪

312
00:19:08,550 --> 00:19:14,592
♪At least the shadow
still makes a person♪
